9
00:01:47,000 --> 00:01:49,457
<i>That's amazing, Santa.
I've got another question...</i>

10
00:01:49,541 --> 00:01:50,541
Hm.

11
00:01:53,375 --> 00:01:55,832
<i>...Deliver Christmas presents
to all the children</i>

12
00:01:55,916 --> 00:01:57,833
<i>- around the world.
- That's right.</i>

13
00:03:03,125 --> 00:03:05,791
Leah

14
00:03:05,875 --> 00:03:07,416
good.

15
00:03:26,250 --> 00:03:28,166
William...

16
00:03:38,416 --> 00:03:40,250
...good.

17
00:03:53,458 --> 00:03:57,208
Stay good.

18
